Description :
        Reborn in pursuit of revenge, I am sure I can easily achieve my goal, as— I happen to be as rich as Bill Gates, as beautiful as Audrey Hepburn, and as deadly as deadpool. However, none of these above works when it comes to dealing with a sweating and panting CEO, who is poisoned, who is in need of “immediate relief.” I’d love to help, but…don’t pull an ice-cool face when you’re kissing me, sir!
